description.$:
Supplementary data 7
To create, take original file, then in R:
tree <- read.tree("1-s2.0-S1055790317300477-mmc7.new")
tips <- strsplit(tree$tip.label, "_")
g <- unlist(lapply(tips, "[", 1))
s <- unlist(lapply(tips, "[", 2))
spp <- paste(g, s, sep="_")
tree2 <- tree
tree2$tip.label <- as.character(spp)
indices <- 1:length(tree$tip.label)
dups <- spp[duplicated(spp)]
toReplace <- indices[tree2$tip.label %in% dups]
tree2$tip.label[tree2$tip.label %in% dups] <- tree$tip.label[toReplace]
write.tree(tree2, "forImport.tree")
